  "texts": [
    "The main plot shows charge density in color (dark spots correspond to AA regions) and complex IVC order parameter ∼ ⟨τxσx⟩ + i ⟨τyσx⟩ in arrows.",
    "Bloch spheres schematically illustrate the different IVC angles across three AA regions.",
    "Insets show the graphene scale charge patterns at three different AA regions.",
    "Blue (red) dots correspond to positive (negative) values of ⟨ĉ † A ĉB ⟩ + ⟨ĉ † B ĉA ⟩, with the cross marking the center of each AA region.",
    "Adapted with permission from Kwan et al., Phys."
  ],
